1.2.name: wordpress/wp-auto-tagger
1.2.description:
This plugin uses the Yahoo API to suggest tags based on the post content. You have the option to automatically tags posts on save or get tag suggestions with a single click. Auto Tagger will not replace your existing tags.

This version has been updated to support Wordpress 2.5. For older versions of Wordpress please download version 1.2.
